FcConfigSetRescanInterval(3)                                                                                                                                                  FcConfigSetRescanInterval(3)

NAME
       FcConfigSetRescanInterval - Set config rescan interval

SYNOPSIS
       #include <fontconfig/fontconfig.h>

       FcBool FcConfigSetRescanInterval (FcConfig *config, int rescanInterval);

DESCRIPTION
       Sets  the  rescan interval. Returns FcFalse if the interval cannot be set (due to allocation failure). Otherwise returns FcTrue.  An interval setting of zero disables automatic checks.  If config
       is NULL, the current configuration is used.

